-Morning!
-Good morning!

199
00:13:51,564 --> 00:13:55,935
Good morning!

200
00:13:56,535 --> 00:14:02,408
<i>In July, the members finally gathered
after ending a long stay-at-home period.</i>

201
00:14:06,011 --> 00:14:08,047
He's grown so much!

202
00:14:08,113 --> 00:14:10,216
Just vertically, so I'm doing a bit of...

203
00:14:10,282 --> 00:14:11,517
No, horizontally too!

204
00:14:11,584 --> 00:14:13,219
You need to work out.

