206
00:14:17,256 --> 00:14:19,592
That alone made me happy.

207
00:14:20,226 --> 00:14:23,095
{\an8}I think that was probably our time

208
00:14:23,162 --> 00:14:26,298
{\an8}to build up our own strengths.

209
00:14:28,901 --> 00:14:33,539
<i>This day's lesson was for "Kumikyoku"
