210
00:14:37,843 --> 00:14:41,380
Opposite of where you're pulled back...

211
00:14:41,447 --> 00:14:44,884
Um, your left shoulder blade
goes the other way.

212
00:14:44,950 --> 00:14:46,986
There's a bit of a mutual pull and...

