00:14:48,687 --> 00:14:53,158
<i>Due to the stay-at-home break,
their bodies won't move as freely.</i>

214
00:14:53,926 --> 00:14:56,795
Like this... Yeah, that's good!

215
00:14:58,397 --> 00:15:01,901
